# Event Explorer App (MVVM + Room + Offline First)

##  Overview
A mobile application that lists nearby events based on user location, allows bookmarking, and works offline with caching.

---

##  Architecture

- MVVM (Model-View-ViewModel)
- Repository Pattern
- Single Source of Truth (Room DB)
- Offline First Approach

---

## Features

- Load events from local JSON (assets)
- Persist data in Room Database
- Bookmark / Remove Bookmark functionality
- Live updates using Flow
- Distance calculation using device location
- Open event location in Google Maps
- Image loading with Glide
- Offline support
- Clean architecture design

---

##  Data Flow

1. App launches
2. ViewModel requests data
3. Repository checks Room DB
4. If empty → loads api → inserts into DB
5. Room emits data via Flow
6. UI updates automatically

---

## ️Bookmark System

- Toggle using Repository
- UI updates automatically via Room Flow

---

## Location Features

- Runtime location permission
- Distance calculation (user → event)
- Open Google Maps via deep link

---

## Tech Stack

- Kotlin
- Room Database
- MVVM Architecture
- Coroutines + Flow
- Hilt Dependency Injection
- Glide
- Google Maps Intent



1.Sequence Diagram (App Startup Flow)
User opens app
     ↓
Request Location Permission
     ↓
User Allows
     ↓
Fetch Location
     ↓
ViewModel.setLocation()
     ↓
Trigger Flow
     ↓
Repository.getEvents()
     ↓
Load from DB → emit
     ↓
Call API
     ↓
Preserve bookmarks
     ↓
Save to DB
     ↓
Emit updated list
     ↓
UI updates RecyclerView

2. Architecture Diagram (MVVM + Clean Data Flow)
                            ┌─────────────────────────────┐
                            │        UI Layer             │
                            │ Activity / Fragment        │
                            └────────────┬────────────────┘
                                         ↓
                            ┌─────────────────────────────┐
                            │       ViewModel (MVVM)      │
                            │ StateFlow / LiveData        │
                            └────────────┬────────────────┘
                                         ↓
                            ┌─────────────────────────────┐
                            │       Repository            │
                            │ (Single Source of Truth)    │
                            └───────┬───────────┬─────────┘
                                    ↓           ↓
                            ┌──────────────┐   ┌──────────────┐
                            │   Room DB    │   │   Retrofit   │
                            │ (Local Data) │   │ (Remote API) │
                            └──────────────┘   └──────────────┘